flowRoot.flowPara: A: Pit Trap triggered by weight, causing the floor to fall away. Cushioned on bottom with spikes painted on the walls.
B: Net Trap triggered by a trip wire. A wide net falls from above. Everyone under has time for 1 reaction before they are caught. The net is covered in large paper mache "carnivorous beetles".
C: Swinging Spikes Trap triggered by pressure plate. A panel with (dull) spikes hinges from the ceiling above, pushing you towards B.
D: Poison Darts Trap triggered by pressure plate. Dull darts shot out of the wall and pelt you.
E: Boiling Oil Trap triggered by trip wires. Water pours over you.
F: Bear Traps. The whole area is very slippery and scattered with (padded) bear traps.
G: Fire Trap triggered by pressure plate. Steam jets out of the half-wall "above" you. It is not hot enough to hurt you.
H: Rock Fall Trap triggered by trip wire. Cushions fall from the ceiling.
stairs up a half-level to rest of shop
